title: Google Pixel 8a - Unlocked Android Phone with Google AI, Advanced Pixel Camera and 24-Hour Battery - Obsidian - 128 GB
description: Meet Pixel 8a. It’s engineered by Google with powerful security and the incredible Pixel Camera. With Google AI, you can do more, even easier – like fix photos, screen calls, and get answers.[7] And it has an all-day battery, so you have power when you need it most.[8] All at a great price.
